le=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73dcdca1e2c412439ce5acdb0ab11b3ec2d48219","tid":1541873,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:37:45.000Z","msg":"感謝三英<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n撤回唔係為咗俾香港人降溫；<br />\n撤回係要分化外國政客、媒體，<br />\n令佢地失去插手香港局面既意慾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人<br />\n約定你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/izm7G7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fizm7G7f.jpg&h=6080f594&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aTJem7g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaTJem7g.jpg&h=c2ef69f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n九月八日 星期日</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n12:30pm <br />\n遮打集合<br />\n<br />\n2:00pm<br />\n<ins>美國駐港澳總領事館</ins> <br />\n為《香港人權及民主法案》請願</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唱國歌